            <h1 class="Slogan">Sketching &amp; GUI Prototyping, FREE &amp; OPEN!</h1><div class="TextContent"><div>With the power of the underlying <strong class="Name">Mozilla Gecko engine</strong>, <strong>Pencil</strong> turns your excellent Firefox 3 browser into a sketching tool with just a 400-kilobyte installation package. <br /><br /><strong>Pencil</strong> will <em>always be free</em> and can run on virtually all platforms that <span class="Name">Firefox 3</span> supports.</div></div><div class="QuickLinks"><a href="Screenshots.html"><strong>Take a Quick Tour</strong></a> Or <a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/8487"><strong>Install It, Now!</strong></a></div>
        
